      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>1218</offset>
        <text>Microautoradiography showed a strong increase in the proportion of Synechococcus cells actively taking up 35S-DMSP, which, after full sunlight exposure, made up to 15% of total active Bacteria.
</text>
        <annotation id="T14">
          <infon key="brat-id">T14</infon>
